    {
      "id": "E:note:row496723:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "63F who presented to OSH ED with flu like symptoms, fever, and SOB.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row496723#s1",
      "text": "63F who presented to OSH ED with flu like symptoms, fever, and SOB."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row496723:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Her    symptoms began Friday [**11-16**] with body aches and a cough.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row496723#s2",
      "text": "Her    symptoms began Friday [**11-16**] with body aches and a cough."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row496723:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "She also    reports an H1N1 outbreak in her area, developed fever to 102 and chi",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row496723#s3",
      "text": "She also    reports an H1N1 outbreak in her area, developed fever to 102 and chills    last night, and today developed wheezing."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row496723:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Cough was dry,    non-productive, Symptoms associated with generalized fatigue a",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row496723#s4",
      "text": "Cough was dry,    non-productive, Symptoms associated with generalized fatigue and    weakness and lightheadedness especially on standing."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row496723:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "She had nausea but    no vomiting, and did have diarrhea x 3 today.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row496723#s5",
      "text": "She had nausea but    no vomiting, and did have diarrhea x 3 today."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row496723:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "She presented to an OSH    ED, where she was noted to be hypoxic to 85% RA, and ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row496723#s6",
      "text": "She presented to an OSH    ED, where she was noted to be hypoxic to 85% RA, and hypotensive to    80s."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row496723:7",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "CXR showed bilat infiltrates.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row496723#s7",
      "text": "CXR showed bilat infiltrates."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row496723:8",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Received 2l IVF CTX, azithro, and    transferred to [**Hospital1 19**].",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row496723#s8",
      "text": "Received 2l IVF CTX, azithro, and    transferred to [**Hospital1 19**]."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row496723:9",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Respiratory failure, acute (not ARDS/[**Doctor Last Name 11**])    Assessment:  ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row496723#s9",
      "text": "Respiratory failure, acute (not ARDS/[**Doctor Last Name 11**])    Assessment:    New admission from ED,confirmed H1N1 from OSH    Afebrile HR 100 s,RR 35-40,unable to lie flat,sats 92-95% on NC 5L    Systolic pressure 100-120 admitted with  levophed  0.04 mic    Action:      Team notified about  tachypnea, NRBM  changed to NC  5L    NS 1L bolus blood culture    On triple antibiotics, awaiting for ID approval for tamiflu    Response:    CVP  4 ,levo turned off,NBP stable    Pt  reports that she is comfortable with her breathing initially after    admission but by 0600 c/o more SOB, I cant relax , informed MD,team  at    bedside to evaluate.NC changed to NRBM ."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row496723:10",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Plan:    Monitor resp status,on droplet precaution.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row496723#s10",
      "text": "Plan:    Monitor resp status,on droplet precaution."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row496723:11",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Supplemental o2 as needed    Possible intubation  for worsening resp status",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row496723#s11",
